                     <interp inst="t18070916-15-person171" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was delivered to me and the flannel at the watchhouse.</p>
               <p>(The property produced and identified.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. As I was coming along I picked it up in the street.</p>
